    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8096-a4ac-cf3a1ea89f58",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ML pipelines are essential to predict students in need and make necessary recommendations often using behavioral logs or demographic data stored in the SIS. This strategy is vulnerable to concept drift or spuriousness. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8096-a4ac-cf3a1ea89f58",
        "parent": {
