    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-806d-b56d-c4bd8ef90689",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors show that Lasso outperforms multiple models in both scenarios. Moreover, a linear regression with 2 new features (handcrafted) outperforms multiple more complex ML models. Authors propose their results as an interesting benchmark for future studies.",
